149
00:14:06,444 --> 00:14:09,013
- And you miss them again.
- I know that feeling.

150
00:14:15,353 --> 00:14:16,584
- Drink some water.
- Okay.

151
00:14:22,964 --> 00:14:26,763
I've been thinking about
what to do in the future.

152
