153
00:14:30,304 --> 00:14:32,834
You film, edit, and upload your own videos.

154
00:14:34,204 --> 00:14:36,444
- What will you film?
- Me.

155
00:14:36,473 --> 00:14:37,772
- You?
- You?

156
00:14:37,773 --> 00:14:38,814
Yes.

157
00:14:39,174 --> 00:14:42,683
